  "description": {
    "S": "This Vietnamese-inspired pho is a quick and aromatic adaptation perfect for busy weeknights. Made with rice noodles, a fragrant broth infused with charred aromatics, and your choice of protein, this comforting bowl delivers authentic flavors in just an hour."
  },
